Dillon said the interest in the Raqqa Internal Security Force is intense and the coalition will continue to screen applicants for training and employment.
The US-led coalition is cooperating with the Syrian Democratic Forces, the main backbone of the PYD/PKK, in the recapture of Raqqa.
